onesian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indonesian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 479, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kepler_object_of_interest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KOI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kepler_object_of_interest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kepler_object_of_interest\"}, {\"begin\": 496, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8234713481707854e-35, \"text\": \"Jakarta\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakarta\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eko\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"a press release\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eko struggled during the snatch attempts.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eko\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"the snatch attempts\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He successfully lifted 135 kg on the second attempt but failed in the first and third (139 kg).\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"135 kg\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the second attempt\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"the first and third (139 kg\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His clean and jerk attempts of 162 kg were also unsuccessful.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His clean and jerk attempts\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"162 kg\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He even fell in the final failed lift and had discomfort in his right thigh.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final failed lift\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"discomfort\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"his right thigh\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eko attributed his subpar performance to a lingering leg injury.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eko\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"his subpar performance\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"a lingering leg injury\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[I have had] knee issues since last year, and also my right thigh [has been injured] for the past month,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"knee issues\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the past month\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indonesian team doctor Andhika Raspati clarified that the injury was not severe and that he could walk despite limping after the competition.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"score\": 0.9999998912571814, \"rank\": 1.0874293037147962e-07, \"text\": \"Indonesian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His condition is not that bad, he can still walk,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His condition\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indonesian Chef de Mission (CdM) Responds The Chef de Mission (CdM) of